body:
Comment 1 by **kenliz@cruzio.com**: 
I've seen the same error messages on a different platform: amd64 darwin
hg identify => 08a7f3163de9 tip (and an earlier release)
The problem package was defining and exporting only types and constants.
Again, the solution was to run:
   gopack grc XYZ.a XYZ.6
after compiling the packages.
One further detail is the work around is to leave the .6 files (for the compile of
main.go).
